contentheadline.headline: List of Governors-General of the Gambia

contentrichtext.text: This page contains a list of '''Governors-General of [[the Gambia]]''' during the period when it was a monarchy, from 1965 to 1970. == Governors-General of the Gambia, 1965-1970 == * [[John Warburton Paul|Sir John Warburton Paul]]: 18 February 1965 - 9 February 1966 * [[Farimang Mamadi Singateh|Sir Farimang Mamadi Singateh]]: 9 February 1966 - 24 April 1970 == See also == {{Portal|The Gambia|Politics}} *[[List of heads of state of the Gambia]] {{Governors-General of the Commonwealth Realms}} {{Commonwealth realms royal reps}} [[Category:Government of the Gambia]] [[Category:History of the Gambia]] [[Category:Lists of governors-general|Gambia, List of Governors-General of The]] [[Category:Governors-General of the Gambia| ]] [[Category:Gambia-related lists|Governors-General]]
